{"thag20.1:0.1":"Theragatha 20.1 ","thag20.1:0.2":"Satthinipata ","thag20.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag20.1:0.4":"Mahamoggallanattheragatha ","thag20.1:1.1":"“Arannika pindapatika, ","thag20.1:1.2":"unchapattagate rata; ","thag20.1:1.3":"Dalemu maccuno senam, ","thag20.1:1.4":"ajjhattam susamahita. ","thag20.1:2.1":"Arannika pindapatika, ","thag20.1:2.2":"unchapattagate rata; ","thag20.1:2.3":"Dhunama maccuno senam, ","thag20.1:2.4":"nalagaramva kunjaro. ","thag20.1:3.1":"Rukkhamulika satatika, ","thag20.1:3.2":"unchapattagate rata; ","thag20.1:3.3":"Dalemu maccuno senam, ","thag20.1:3.4":"ajjhattam susamahita. ","thag20.1:4.1":"Rukkhamulika satatika, ","thag20.1:4.2":"unchapattagate rata; ","thag20.1:4.3":"Dhunama maccuno senam, ","thag20.1:4.4":"nalagaramva kunjaro”. ","thag20.1:5.1":"“Atthikankalakutike, ","thag20.1:5.2":"mamsanharupasibbite; ","thag20.1:5.3":"Dhiratthu pure duggandhe, ","thag20.1:5.4":"paragatte mamayase. ","thag20.1:6.1":"Guthabhaste taconaddhe, ","thag20.1:6.2":"uragandipisacini; ","thag20.1:6.3":"Nava sotani te kaye, ","thag20.1:6.4":"yani sandanti sabbada. ","thag20.1:7.1":"Tava sariram navasotam, ","thag20.1:7.2":"Duggandhakaram paribandham; ","thag20.1:7.3":"Bhikkhu parivajjayate tam, ","thag20.1:7.4":"Milham ca yatha sucikamo. ","thag20.1:8.1":"Evance tam jano janna, ","thag20.1:8.2":"yatha janami tam aham; ","thag20.1:8.3":"Araka parivajjeyya, ","thag20.1:8.4":"guthatthanamva pavuse”. ","thag20.1:9.1":"“Evametam mahavira, ","thag20.1:9.2":"yatha samana bhasasi; ","thag20.1:9.3":"Ettha ceke visidanti, ","thag20.1:9.4":"pankamhiva jaraggavo”. ","thag20.1:10.1":"“Akasamhi haliddiya, ","thag20.1:10.2":"yo mannetha rajetave; ","thag20.1:10.3":"Annena vapi rangena, ","thag20.1:10.4":"vighatudayameva tam. ","thag20.1:11.1":"Tadakasasamam cittam, ","thag20.1:11.2":"ajjhattam susamahitam; ","thag20.1:11.3":"Ma papacitte asadi, ","thag20.1:11.4":"aggikhandhamva pakkhima”. ","thag20.1:12.1":"“Passa cittakatam bimbam, ","thag20.1:12.2":"arukayam samussitam; ","thag20.1:12.3":"Aturam bahusankappam, ","thag20.1:12.4":"yassa natthi dhuvam thiti. ","thag20.1:13.1":"Passa cittakatam rupam, ","thag20.1:13.2":"manina kundalena ca; ","thag20.1:13.3":"Atthim tacena onaddham, ","thag20.1:13.4":"saha vatthehi sobhati. ","thag20.1:14.1":"Alattakakata pada, ","thag20.1:14.2":"mukham cunnakamakkhitam; ","thag20.1:14.3":"Alam balassa mohaya, ","thag20.1:14.4":"no ca paragavesino. ","thag20.1:15.1":"Atthapadakata kesa, ","thag20.1:15.2":"netta anjanamakkhita; ","thag20.1:15.3":"Alam balassa mohaya, ","thag20.1:15.4":"no ca paragavesino. ","thag20.1:16.1":"Anjaniva nava citta, ","thag20.1:16.2":"putikayo alankato; ","thag20.1:16.3":"Alam balassa mohaya, ","thag20.1:16.4":"no ca paragavesino. ","thag20.1:17.1":"Odahi migavo pasam, ","thag20.1:17.2":"nasada vaguram migo; ","thag20.1:17.3":"Bhutva nivapam gacchama, ","thag20.1:17.4":"kaddante migabandhake. ","thag20.1:18.1":"Chinno paso migavassa, ","thag20.1:18.2":"nasada vaguram migo; ","thag20.1:18.3":"Bhutva nivapam gacchama, ","thag20.1:18.4":"socante migaluddake”. ","thag20.1:19.1":"“Tadasi yam bhimsanakam, ","thag20.1:19.2":"tadasi lomahamsanam; ","thag20.1:19.3":"Anekakarasampanne, ","thag20.1:19.4":"sariputtamhi nibbute. ","thag20.1:20.1":"Anicca vata sankhara, ","thag20.1:20.2":"uppadavayadhammino; ","thag20.1:20.3":"Upajjitva nirujjhanti, ","thag20.1:20.4":"tesam vupasamo sukho. ","thag20.1:21.1":"Sukhumam te pativijjhanti, ","thag20.1:21.2":"valaggam usuna yatha; ","thag20.1:21.3":"Ye pancakkhandhe passanti, ","thag20.1:21.4":"parato no ca attato. ","thag20.1:22.1":"Ye ca passanti sankhare, ","thag20.1:22.2":"parato no ca attato; ","thag20.1:22.3":"Paccabyadhimsu nipunam, ","thag20.1:22.4":"valaggam usuna yatha. ","thag20.1:23.1":"Sattiya viya omattho, ","thag20.1:23.2":"dayhamanova matthake; ","thag20.1:23.3":"Kamaragappahanaya, ","thag20.1:23.4":"sato bhikkhu paribbaje. ","thag20.1:24.1":"Sattiya viya omattho, ","thag20.1:24.2":"dayhamanova matthake; ","thag20.1:24.3":"Bhavaragappahanaya, ","thag20.1:24.4":"sato bhikkhu paribbaje. ","thag20.1:25.1":"Codito bhavitattena, ","thag20.1:25.2":"sarirantimadharina; ","thag20.1:25.3":"Migaramatupasadam, ","thag20.1:25.4":"padangutthena kampayim. ","thag20.1:26.1":"Nayidam sithilamarabbha, ","thag20.1:26.2":"nayidam appena thamasa; ","thag20.1:26.3":"Nibbanamadhigantabbam, ","thag20.1:26.4":"sabbaganthapamocanam. ","thag20.1:27.1":"Ayanca daharo bhikkhu, ","thag20.1:27.2":"ayamuttamaporiso; ","thag20.1:27.3":"Dhareti antimam deham, ","thag20.1:27.4":"jetva maram savahinim. ","thag20.1:28.1":"Vivaramanupabhanti vijjuta, ","thag20.1:28.2":"Vebharassa ca pandavassa ca; ","thag20.1:28.3":"Nagavivaragato jhayati, ","thag20.1:28.4":"Putto appatimassa tadino. ","thag20.1:29.1":"Upasanto uparato, ","thag20.1:29.2":"pantasenasano muni; ","thag20.1:29.3":"Dayado buddhasetthassa, ","thag20.1:29.4":"brahmuna abhivandito”. ","thag20.1:30.1":"“Upasantam uparatam, ","thag20.1:30.2":"pantasenasanam munim; ","thag20.1:30.3":"Dayadam buddhasetthassa, ","thag20.1:30.4":"vanda brahmana kassapam. ","thag20.1:31.1":"Yo ca jatisatam gacche, ","thag20.1:31.2":"sabba brahmanajatiyo; ","thag20.1:31.3":"Sottiyo vedasampanno, ","thag20.1:31.4":"manussesu punappunam. ","thag20.1:32.1":"Ajjhayakopi ce assa, ","thag20.1:32.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","thag20.1:32.3":"Etassa vandanayetam, ","thag20.1:32.4":"kalam nagghati solasim. ","thag20.1:33.1":"Yo so attha vimokkhani, ","thag20.1:33.2":"purebhattam aphassayi; ","thag20.1:33.3":"Anulomam patilomam, ","thag20.1:33.4":"tato pindaya gacchati. ","thag20.1:34.1":"Tadisam bhikkhum masadi, ","thag20.1:34.2":"mattanam khani brahmana; ","thag20.1:34.3":"Abhippasadehi manam, ","thag20.1:34.4":"arahantamhi tadine; ","thag20.1:34.5":"Khippam panjaliko vanda, ","thag20.1:34.6":"ma te vijati matthakam”. ","thag20.1:35.1":"“Neso passati saddhammam, ","thag20.1:35.2":"samsarena purakkhato; ","thag20.1:35.3":"Adhogamam jimhapatham, ","thag20.1:35.4":"kummaggamanudhavati. ","thag20.1:36.1":"Kimiva milhasallitto, ","thag20.1:36.2":"sankhare adhimucchito; ","thag20.1:36.3":"Pagalho labhasakkare, ","thag20.1:36.4":"tuccho gacchati potthilo”. ","thag20.1:37.1":"“Imanca passa ayantam, ","thag20.1:37.2":"sariputtam sudassanam; ","thag20.1:37.3":"Vimuttam ubhatobhage, ","thag20.1:37.4":"ajjhattam susamahitam. ","thag20.1:38.1":"Visallam khinasamyogam, ","thag20.1:38.2":"tevijjam maccuhayinam; ","thag20.1:38.3":"Dakkhineyyam manussanam, ","thag20.1:38.4":"punnakkhettam anuttaram”. ","thag20.1:39.1":"“Ete sambahula deva, ","thag20.1:39.2":"iddhimanto yasassino; ","thag20.1:39.3":"Dasa devasahassani, ","thag20.1:39.4":"sabbe brahmapurohita; ","thag20.1:39.5":"Moggallanam namassanta, ","thag20.1:39.6":"titthanti panjalikata. ","thag20.1:40.1":"‘Namo te purisajanna, ","thag20.1:40.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","thag20.1:40.3":"Yassa te asava khina, ","thag20.1:40.4":"dakkhineyyosi marisa’. ","thag20.1:41.1":"Pujito naradevena, ","thag20.1:41.2":"uppanno maranabhibhu; ","thag20.1:41.3":"Pundarikamva toyena, ","thag20.1:41.4":"sankharenupalippati. ","thag20.1:42.1":"Yassa muhuttena sahassadha loko, ","thag20.1:42.2":"Samvidito sabrahmakappo vasi; ","thag20.1:42.3":"Iddhigune cutupapate kale, ","thag20.1:42.4":"Passati devata sa bhikkhu”. ","thag20.1:43.1":"“Sariputtova pannaya, ","thag20.1:43.2":"silena upasamena ca; ","thag20.1:43.3":"Yopi parangato bhikkhu, ","thag20.1:43.4":"etavaparamo siya. ","thag20.1:44.1":"Kotisatasahassassa, ","thag20.1:44.2":"Attabhavam khanena nimmine; ","thag20.1:44.3":"Aham vikubbanasu kusalo, ","thag20.1:44.4":"Vasibhutomhi iddhiya. ","thag20.1:45.1":"Samadhivijjavasiparamigato, ","thag20.1:45.2":"Moggallanagotto asitassa sasane; ","thag20.1:45.3":"Dhiro samucchindi samahitindriyo, ","thag20.1:45.4":"Nago yatha putilatamva bandhanam. ","thag20.1:46.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag20.1:46.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thag20.1:46.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thag20.1:46.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thag20.1:47.1":"Yassa catthaya pabbajito, ","thag20.1:47.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag20.1:47.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thag20.1:47.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thag20.1:48.1":"Kidiso nirayo asi, ","thag20.1:48.2":"yattha dussi apaccatha; ","thag20.1:48.3":"Vidhuram savakamasajja, ","thag20.1:48.4":"kakusandhanca brahmanam. ","thag20.1:49.1":"Satam asi ayosanku, ","thag20.1:49.2":"sabbe paccattavedana; ","thag20.1:49.3":"Idiso nirayo asi, ","thag20.1:49.4":"yattha dussi apaccatha; ","thag20.1:49.5":"Vidhuram savakamasajja, ","thag20.1:49.6":"kakusandhanca brahmanam. ","thag20.1:50.1":"Yo etamabhijanati, ","thag20.1:50.2":"bhikkhu buddhassa savako; ","thag20.1:50.3":"Tadisam bhikkhumasajja, ","thag20.1:50.4":"kanha dukkham nigacchasi. ","thag20.1:51.1":"Majjhesarasmim titthanti, ","thag20.1:51.2":"vimana kappathayino; ","thag20.1:51.3":"Veluriyavanna rucira, ","thag20.1:51.4":"accimanto pabhassara; ","thag20.1:51.5":"Acchara tattha naccanti, ","thag20.1:51.6":"puthu nanattavanniyo. ","thag20.1:52.1":"Yo etamabhijanati, ","thag20.1:52.2":"… pe ","thag20.1:52.3":"… ","thag20.1:52.4":"kanha dukkham nigacchasi. ","thag20.1:53.1":"Yo ve buddhena codito, ","thag20.1:53.2":"bhikkhusanghassa pekkhato; ","thag20.1:53.3":"Migaramatupasadam, ","thag20.1:53.4":"padangutthena kampayi. ","thag20.1:54.1":"Yo etamabhijanati, ","thag20.1:54.2":"… pe ","thag20.1:54.3":"… ","thag20.1:54.4":"kanha dukkham nigacchasi. ","thag20.1:55.1":"Yo vejayantapasadam, ","thag20.1:55.2":"padangutthena kampayi; ","thag20.1:55.3":"Iddhibalenupatthaddho, ","thag20.1:55.4":"samvejesi ca devata. ","thag20.1:56.1":"Yo etamabhijanati, ","thag20.1:56.2":"… pe ","thag20.1:56.3":"… ","thag20.1:56.4":"kanha dukkham nigacchasi. ","thag20.1:57.1":"Yo vejayantapasade, ","thag20.1:57.2":"sakkam so paripucchati; ","thag20.1:57.3":"Api avuso janasi, ","thag20.1:57.4":"tanhakkhayavimuttiyo; ","thag20.1:57.5":"Tassa sakko viyakasi, ","thag20.1:57.6":"panham puttho yathatatham”. ","thag20.1:58.1":"“Yo etamabhijanati, ","thag20.1:58.2":"… pe ","thag20.1:58.3":"… ","thag20.1:58.4":"kanha dukkham nigacchasi. ","thag20.1:59.1":"Yo brahmanam paripucchati, ","thag20.1:59.2":"Sudhammayam thito sabham; ","thag20.1:59.3":"Ajjapi tyavuso sa ditthi, ","thag20.1:59.4":"Ya te ditthi pure ahu; ","thag20.1:59.5":"Passasi vitivattantam, ","thag20.1:59.6":"Brahmaloke pabhassaram. ","thag20.1:60.1":"Tassa brahma viyakasi, ","thag20.1:60.2":"panham puttho yathatatham; ","thag20.1:60.3":"Na me marisa sa ditthi, ","thag20.1:60.4":"ya me ditthi pure ahu. ","thag20.1:61.1":"Passami vitivattantam, ","thag20.1:61.2":"brahmaloke pabhassaram; ","thag20.1:61.3":"Soham ajja katham vajjam, ","thag20.1:61.4":"aham niccomhi sassato”. ","thag20.1:62.1":"“Yo etamabhijanati, ","thag20.1:62.2":"… pe ","thag20.1:62.3":"… ","thag20.1:62.4":"kanha dukkham nigacchasi. ","thag20.1:63.1":"Yo mahaneruno kutam, ","thag20.1:63.2":"vimokkhena aphassayi; ","thag20.1:63.3":"Vanam pubbavidehanam, ","thag20.1:63.4":"ye ca bhumisaya nara. ","thag20.1:64.1":"Yo etamabhijanati, ","thag20.1:64.2":"bhikkhu buddhassa savako; ","thag20.1:64.3":"Tadisam bhikkhumasajja, ","thag20.1:64.4":"kanha dukkham nigacchasi. ","thag20.1:65.1":"Na ve aggi cetayati, ","thag20.1:65.2":"aham balam dahamiti; ","thag20.1:65.3":"Balova jalitam aggim, ","thag20.1:65.4":"asajja nam padayhati. ","thag20.1:66.1":"Evamevam tuvam mara, ","thag20.1:66.2":"asajja nam tathagatam; ","thag20.1:66.3":"Sayam dahissasi attanam, ","thag20.1:66.4":"balo aggimva samphusam. ","thag20.1:67.1":"Apunnam pasavi maro, ","thag20.1:67.2":"asajja nam tathagatam; ","thag20.1:67.3":"Kim nu mannasi papima, ","thag20.1:67.4":"na me papam vipaccati. ","thag20.1:68.1":"Karato te ciyate papam, ","thag20.1:68.2":"cirarattaya antaka; ","thag20.1:68.3":"Mara nibbinda buddhamha, ","thag20.1:68.4":"asam makasi bhikkhusu”. ","thag20.1:69.1":"“Iti maram atajjesi, ","thag20.1:69.2":"bhikkhu bhesakalavane; ","thag20.1:69.3":"Tato so dummano yakkho, ","thag20.1:69.4":"tatthevantaradhayatha”ti. ","thag20.1:69.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma mahamoggallano thero gathayo abhasitthati. ","thag20.1:69.6":"Satthinipato nitthito. ","thag20.1:70.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag20.1:70.1":"Satthikamhi nipatamhi, ","thag20.1:70.2":"moggallano mahiddhiko; ","thag20.1:70.3":"Ekova theragathayo, ","thag20.1:70.4":"atthasatthi bhavanti tati. "}